OL,3,CDo criminal gangs control Britain's
OL,4,Cprisons?
OL,6,FJohn Podmore, who was the governor at
OL,7,Fthree different prisons in the UK and
OL,8,Fheaded the Corruption Prevention Unit
OL,9,Facross the entire prison service,
OL,10,Fwarned that prison governors and
OL,11,Fofficers are no longer in charge.
OL,13,FThe problem, according to Podmore, is
OL,14,Fbeing fuelled by the prison drug
OL,15,Ftrade, which he estimates is worth #1
OL,16,Fbillion a year.
OL,18,F"Staff will be the primary source in
OL,19,Fmost prisons", Podmore said.
