OL,6,FMeanwhile, Pia Sinha, who also
OL,7,Fgoverned three prisons, echoed
OL,8,FPodmore's sentiment, telling ITV News
OL,9,F"overrun and overcrowded" jails have
OL,10,Feffectively led to a "vacuum of
OL,11,Fleadership...filled by criminality".
OL,13,F"The drug trade in prisons in this
OL,14,Fcountry across all prisons is probably
OL,15,Fworth about #1 billion"
OL,17,FInsiders who've spoken to ITV News
OL,18,Fhave also raised questions about the
OL,19,Fvetting process, training and support
OL,20,Ffor prison staff.
